---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = 'The AI-Powered Agile Blueprint';
const pageDescription = 'How I got rehired in 2 weeks after being laid off with thousands of other Scrum Masters. Get the free blueprint with my exact 3-phase roadmap.';
---

<LandingLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <!-- Hero Section - Dark background like FirstMovers -->
  <section class="relative bg-[#0a0a0a] overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Subtle gradient overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/20 via-transparent to-purple-900/10"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 pt-20 pb-24 sm:pt-28 sm:pb-32 lg:pt-36 lg:pb-40">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <!-- Personal intro -->
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-blue-400 font-medium mb-6">
          Hi, I'm Danny.
        </p>

        <!-- Main headline -->
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-8" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          How I Got Rehired in 2 Weeks After Being Laid Off With Thousands of Other Scrum Masters
        </h1>

        <!-- Hook statement -->
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          When companies started cutting "ceremony-only" agile roles in January 2023, I built automation systems that proved I was technical—not "just a facilitator."
        </p>

        <!-- Value prop -->
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-white font-semibold mb-10">
          This free blueprint is my exact 3-phase roadmap.
        </p>

        <!-- CTA Button -->
        <button
          type="button"
          data-modal-trigger="blueprint"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-5 text-lg font-bold text-white rounded-full transition-all duration-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-500/50 hover:scale-105"
          style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #294bf3 0%, #1e3a8a 100%); box-shadow: 0 10px 40px -10px rgba(41, 75, 243, 0.5);"
        >
          Get The Blueprint
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Crisis Story Section - Two column on desktop -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">
        <!-- Text Column -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1a1a] leading-tight mb-8" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
            My Layoff Should Have Been Career-Ending. Instead, I Was Back at Work in 2 Weeks.
          </h2>

          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-6">
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
              In January 2023, companies made a choice:
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Keep the agile professionals who "just facilitated meetings" or keep the ones who "built technical systems."
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
              I was laid off along with thousands of other Scrum Masters. My peers spent months searching for interviews. Some are still looking.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a]">
              But I was back at work within two weeks—landing a Fortune 500 pharmaceutical role.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Quote/Highlight Column -->
        <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-32">
          <div class="bg-[#f0f7ff] rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border-l-4 border-[#294bf3]">
            <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] leading-relaxed mb-6">
              The difference?
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              In every interview, I could say:
            </p>
            <blockquote class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-[#1a1a1a] font-medium italic leading-relaxed border-l-0 pl-0">
              "I've built Jira automation systems that saved my last team 12 hours per sprint. I don't just coordinate work—I architect solutions that create measurable value."
            </blockquote>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-6">
              That's not facilitation. That's technical proof.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl font-bold text-[#294bf3] mt-6">
              So I made a different choice. I built systems that made me indispensable.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Inline Email Form #1 - Grey background section like FirstMovers -->
  <section class="bg-[#f0f7ff]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-24">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4" style="letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
            Get The AI-Powered Agile Blueprint
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            The 3-Phase Transformation: From Manual Coordinator to AI-Powered Architect
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Email Form -->
        <form class="space-y-4 mb-6">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <input
              type="email"
              placeholder="Enter your email"
              class="flex-1 px-5 py-4 border border-gray-300 rounded-xl text-lg text-gray-900 placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#294bf3] focus:border-transparent transition-all"
              required
            />
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 whitespace-nowrap"
              style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #294bf3 0%, #1e3a8a 100%);"
            >
              Download The Blueprint
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>

        <!-- Social Proof -->
        <p class="text-center text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          I've trained <strong class="text-[#1a1a1a]">15,000+ agile professionals</strong> across 130 countries. This is the exact roadmap that creates career optionality—not just certifications.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proof/Results Section -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1a1a] leading-tight mb-8 text-center" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          My Automation Systems Never Stop Working. They Don't Take Sick Days. They Just Create Value.
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8 text-center">
          While other Scrum Masters were updating Jira tickets manually, my automation systems were:
        </p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-10">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-[#f0f7ff] rounded-xl p-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-[#1a1a1a] font-medium">Syncing sprint dates automatically</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-[#f0f7ff] rounded-xl p-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-[#1a1a1a] font-medium">Prepping standup updates before meetings</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-[#f0f7ff] rounded-xl p-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-[#1a1a1a] font-medium">Flagging blockers 3 days before they became crises</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-[#f0f7ff] rounded-xl p-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#294bf3] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-[#1a1a1a] font-medium">Sending stakeholder reports without human intervention</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#0a0a0a] rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            I quickly realized this wasn't just about efficiency—it was about separating your value from your hours.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white">
            Companies don't want coordinators anymore. They want architects who build systems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Inside Section -->
  <section class="bg-[#f0f7ff]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-4" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          Get My Career Survival Blueprint.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          This blueprint gives you the exact frameworks I built when my career was on the line. Inside, you'll get:
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA above frameworks -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <button
          type="button"
          data-modal-trigger="blueprint"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-5 text-lg font-bold text-white rounded-full transition-all duration-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-500/50 hover:scale-105"
          style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #294bf3 0%, #1e3a8a 100%); box-shadow: 0 10px 40px -10px rgba(41, 75, 243, 0.5);"
        >
          I Need This Blueprint
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- 6 Framework Cards - 2x3 grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8 mb-16">
        <!-- Framework 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-2">
                The 3-Phase Transformation Path
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                The exact career progression from Manual Coordinator → Automation Builder → Agentic Strategist → AI-Powered Architect. Includes time investment for each phase, skills to develop, and career impact at every stage.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-2">
                The 5 Automation Patterns That Prove You're Technical
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                The Sprint Sync Engine, 12-Minute Standup, Stale Ticket Radar, and automated reporting systems that saved my teams 12+ hours per sprint—and got me hired in 2 weeks.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-2">
                The Interview Answer Framework
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                The exact responses I used when interviewers asked "How do you ensure data accuracy?" and "How do you identify blockers early?" You'll sound technical, not like a meeting facilitator.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-2">
                The Self-Assessment Quiz
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Identify where you are right now: Manual Coordinator, Automation Builder, Agentic Strategist, or AI-Powered Architect. Know your starting point to plan your path forward.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-2">
                The Career Insurance Checklist
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                The 10 technical skills that make you layoff-resistant in 2026. Plus: which skills to prioritize based on your current role (Scrum Master, Product Owner, RTE, Agile Coach).
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Framework 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-[#294bf3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-2">
                The First 30 Days Roadmap
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Week-by-week action plan to build your first automation system, prove technical value to your team, and start repositioning yourself as an architect (not just a facilitator).
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PDF Visual Placeholder -->
      <div class="max-w-md mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-2xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-gradient-to-br from-[#294bf3] to-[#1e3a8a] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <div class="text-center text-white p-6">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 opacity-80" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
              <p class="text-xl font-bold">AI-Powered Agile Blueprint</p>
              <p class="text-sm opacity-80 mt-2">The 3-Phase Transformation</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-center text-gray-500 text-sm">Free PDF Guide • Instant Download</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final Closer Section -->
  <section class="bg-[#0a0a0a]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-8" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
        Your Career Is Too Important to Be Limited by Facilitation Skills.
      </h2>

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Whether you've been laid off, fear being replaced by AI, or simply want career optionality instead of job dependency—the path is the same.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Companies aren't cutting agile roles because agile is dead. They're cutting roles that "just coordinate."
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-white font-semibold">
          The professionals who survive and thrive are the ones who can prove they build systems, architect solutions, and create technical value.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xl text-[#00a8cc] font-semibold mb-10">
        This blueprint is your first step.
      </p>

      <!-- Final CTA -->
      <button
        type="button"
        data-modal-trigger="blueprint"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-12 py-6 text-xl font-bold text-white rounded-full transition-all duration-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-500/50 hover:scale-105"
        style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #294bf3 0%, #1e3a8a 100%); box-shadow: 0 10px 40px -10px rgba(41, 75, 243, 0.5);"
      >
        Send Me The Blueprint
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Popup Modal -->
  <div
    id="blueprint-modal"
    class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden"
    role="dialog"
    aria-modal="true"
    aria-labelledby="modal-title"
  >
    <!-- Backdrop with blur -->
    <div
      id="modal-backdrop"
      class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/70 backdrop-blur-sm transition-opacity"
      aria-hidden="true"
    ></div>

    <!-- Modal Panel -->
    <div class="fixed inset-0 overflow-y-auto">
      <div class="flex min-h-full items-center justify-center p-4 sm:p-6">
        <div
          id="modal-panel"
          class="relative w-full max-w-lg transform overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-2xl transition-all"
        >
          <!-- Close Button -->
          <button
            id="modal-close-button"
            type="button"
            class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#294bf3] rounded-lg p-2 z-10"
            aria-label="Close modal"
          >
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
            </svg>
          </button>

          <!-- Modal Content -->
          <div class="px-6 py-10 sm:px-10 sm:py-12">
            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
